303
00:18:12,360 --> 00:18:13,000
Run fast.

304
00:18:13,000 --> 00:18:14,920
There's a fight. Everybody run.

305
00:18:15,080 --> 00:18:15,720
Move.

306
00:18:22,730 --> 00:18:23,320
Run fast.

307
00:18:23,680 --> 00:18:24,400
