530
00:29:58,720 --> 00:29:59,400
OK.

531
00:30:02,160 --> 00:30:03,800
Gu, you're clear headed.

532
00:30:04,320 --> 00:30:06,880
A former performer

533
00:30:07,120 --> 00:30:08,920
